Problem Statement

Why are we winning or losing? How often do we win against competitors, or in the enterprise? The answers to these questions are crucial to understand on how to build a successful sales team.
Few sales leaders would say theyâ€™re satisfied with their win rate. In most companies, a good  win rate per sales rep is 47%, and any win rate below is 20% is not good. The question is, is your low win rate due to poor lead and opportunity qualification, or incompetent sales rep? With the win rate and Y0Y comparison, company will be able to track which sales rep brings in more revenue for the company.
